<text><body>
<pb ed="X" id="X02.0181.0835b" n="0835b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0835b01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0835b02"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0835b03"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0835b04"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0835b05"/><head type="no">No. 181</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0835b06"/><juan fun="open" n="1"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead>大聖妙吉祥菩薩最勝威德祕密八
<lb ed="X" n="0835b07"/>字陀羅尼修行念誦儀軌次第法</jhead></juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0835b08"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0835b09"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0835b10"/><div1><p id="pX02p0835b1001">我今依真言次第法門說行人先當從阿闍梨得受
<lb ed="X" n="0835b11"/>灌頂及親傳受<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>乃再入持明悉地灌頂具足慈悲
<lb ed="X" n="0835b12"/>行無緣慈怜愍一切苦厄有情作此念誦誓當<note n="0835001" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB17465;挍疑救拔</note>&CB17465;挍
<lb ed="X" n="0835b13"/>一切恐怖厄難眾生若眾生苦厄難時隨其處或香
<lb ed="X" n="0835b14"/>塗或撚粉作壇若常念者應須<note n="0835002" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">精疑清</note>精室如法建立道場
<lb ed="X" n="0835b15"/>一切如前法行人先興八種心方可持法第一慈悲
<lb ed="X" n="0835b16"/>心二無垢心三無我所心四無勝<note n="0835003" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">附疑負</note>附心五有平等心
<lb ed="X" n="0835b17"/>六無怨害心七有哀愍心八無貪利心如是之人萬
<lb ed="X" n="0835b18"/>可傳受如是等堪同作法若非此者惟應自作令法
<lb ed="X" n="0835b19"/>得成若遍數未終不得中間&CB00364;共人語使有間斷即
<lb ed="X" n="0835b20"/>法失驗未作法時先當明告若自作念誦亦勿間斷
<lb ed="X" n="0835b21"/>行者若入道場時應&CB05418;誠作禮即金剛合掌至心想
<lb ed="X" n="0835b22"/>於十方諸佛及文殊大聖無量菩薩金剛密&CB00528;一切
<lb ed="X" n="0835b23"/>賢聖等前一一自身而禮聖眾普禮一切佛菩薩金
<lb ed="X" n="0835b24"/>剛等真言曰。</p>
<pb ed="X" id="X02.0181.0835c" n="0835c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c01"/><p id="pX02p0835c0101" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>薩&CB00085;<note place="inline">轉舌</note>怛佗<note place="inline">引</note>蘗多<note place="inline">二</note>迦耶&CB00085;訖唧<note place="inline">二合</note>多<note place="inline">三</note>&CB00085;
<lb ed="X" n="0835c02"/><note place="inline">無撥反</note>折羅<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;羅<note place="inline">二合</note>梅<note place="inline">輕呼</note><note place="inline">四</note>曼祖室利<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;嗓那<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c03"/>南<note place="inline">五</note>迦嚕弭</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c04"/><p id="pX02p0835c0401">又心密明曰。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c05"/><p id="pX02p0835c0501" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">日</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">曰</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>微<note place="inline">微一反</note>多</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c06"/><lg id="lgX02p0835c0601"><l>先合金剛掌</l><l>十度外相交</l><l>五輪皆委地</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c07"/><l>至誠恭敬禮</l><l>復以長跪坐</l><l>合掌似合蓮</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c08"/><l>觀身如水精</l><l>吽字如三處</l><l>想成五智杵</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c09"/><l>所謂內金剛</l><l>而為不壞體</l><l>然<note n="0835004" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">處疑虔</note>處誠奉請</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c10"/><l>一切諸聖尊</l><l>誦是四句偈</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c11"/><lg id="lgX02p0835c1101"><l>稽首無上法醫王</l><l>難<note n="0835005" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">教疑救</note>教能救慈悲主</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c12"/><l>我今歸命恭敬請</l><l>唯願速來降道場</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c13"/><lg id="lgX02p0835c1301"><l>如是三重請</l><l>作前啟白言</l><l>二手蓮華合</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c14"/><l>復誦淨三業</l><l>令身器清淨</l><l>用加持五處</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c15"/><l>額兩肩心喉</l><l>念彼真言曰</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c16"/><p id="pX02p0835c1601" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note>縛戍&CB00499;<note place="inline">引</note>薩&CB00085;達磨娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>戍度
<lb ed="X" n="0835c17"/>&CB00805;<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c18"/><lg id="lgX02p0835c1801"><l><app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>淨三業竟</l><l>結佛三昧耶</l><l>定慧合蓮掌</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c19"/><l>開合二火&CB00123;</l><l>二風屈上節</l><l>二空捻風根</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c20"/><l>與印當額前</l><l>諦觀一切佛</l><l>一一分明見</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c21"/><l>住在&CB00980;空中</l><l>念彼真言曰</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c22"/><l>佛部三昧耶</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c23"/><l>定慧內合拳</l><l>二空皆並&CB00594;</l><l>諦觀一切佛</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0835c24"/><l>由如對目前</l><l>隨念召請尊</l><l>雙拳而並召</l></lg>
<pb ed="X" id="X02.0181.0836a" n="0836a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a01"/><p id="pX02p0836a0101" rend="margin-left:2em">真言曰。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a02"/><p id="pX02p0836a0201" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>爾<note place="inline">慈以反</note>曩匿<note place="inline">而翼反</note>迦<note place="inline">半音</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三遍或七遍</note></p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a03"/><lg id="lgX02p0836a0301"><l>復結蓮華部</l><l>祕密三昧耶</l><l>印相亦如前</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a04"/><l>左入右舒出</l><l>三誦三召請</l><l>安右而散之</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a05"/><l>念彼真言曰</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a06"/><p id="pX02p0836a0601" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>嚧力迦<note place="inline">半音</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a07"/><lg id="lgX02p0836a0701"><l>復次金剛部</l><l>微妙三昧契</l><l>前契改空輪</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a08"/><l>右入左&CB00594;招</l><l>專心存念尊</l><l>念彼真言曰</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a09"/><p id="pX02p0836a0901" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>縛<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">日</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">曰</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>地力<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">半音</note><note place="inline">呼</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a10"/><lg id="lgX02p0836a1001"><l>佛部印安額</l><l>蓮華右耳邊</l><l>金剛左耳邊</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a11"/><l>同於頂上散</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a12"/><l>復次被甲契</l><l>檀慧及戒方</l><l>相叉內入掌</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a13"/><l>忍願頭相合</l><l>進力曲如鉤</l><l>外附二火後</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a14"/><l>禪智並直&CB00594;</l><l>由如&CB00085;折羅</l><l>念加身五處</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a15"/><l>額右肩并左</l><l>心喉散頂門</l><l>念彼真言曰</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a16"/><p id="pX02p0836a1601" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>斫羯羅<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00467;<note place="inline">轉舌</note><note place="inline">呼</note>&CB00069;底<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;羅<note place="inline">二合</note>賒弭多<note place="inline">引</note>羅
<lb ed="X" n="0836a17"/>捺羅<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">二合</note>羅<note place="inline">引</note>捺羅<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note>娑摩<note place="inline">二合</note>捺<note place="inline">倉&CB04189;反</note>路<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0836001" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">慧疑瑟</note>慧
<lb ed="X" n="0836a18"/>抳<note place="inline">二合</note>娑路乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>洛乞娑<note place="inline">二合</note>鋡吽發吒娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訶</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a19"/><p id="pX02p0836a1901">次說金剛地界橛印。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a20"/><lg id="lgX02p0836a2001"><l>定手方願度</l><l>雙入戒忍門</l><l>方祕絞戒後</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a21"/><l>入於檀戒間</l><l>願絞入忍進</l><l>檀慧與進力</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a22"/><l>禪智各相合</l><l>三旋下丁之</l><l>即念真言曰</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0836a23"/><p id="pX02p0836a2301" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>枳里枳里&CB00085;<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">日</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">曰</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;曰里<note place="inline">二合</note>步&CB02976;滿<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00499;滿
<lb ed="X" n="0836a24"/>&CB00499;吽<note place="inline">引</note>發吒</p>
<pb ed="X" id="X02.0181.0836b" n="0836b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b01"/><p id="pX02p0836b0101">復說金剛椄犰L。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b02"/><lg id="lgX02p0836b0201"><l>準前地界印</l><l>&CB03370;開禪智&CB00594;</l><l>右旋如棪|</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b03"/><l>隨誦而轉之</l><l>心想金剛</l><l>念彼真言曰</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b04"/><p id="pX02p0836b0401" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>薩羅薩羅&CB00085;日羅<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;羅<note place="inline">二合</note>迦羅<note place="inline">引</note>吽發吒</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b05"/><lg id="lgX02p0836b0501"><l>復次&CB00980;空藏</l><l>十度外相交</l><l>進力&CB17467;如寶</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b06"/><l>想成妙樓閣</l><l>上有大蓮華</l><l>諦心觀本尊</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b07"/><l>住於寶帳中</l><l>周匝幢幡蓋</l><l>天衣香雲海</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b08"/><l>遍滿於&CB00980;空</l><l>眷屬中圍繞</l><l>誦是真言曰</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b09"/><p id="pX02p0836b0901" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;&CB00344;曩三婆<note place="inline">去</note><note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;&CB00085;<note place="inline">無撥反</note>曰囉<note place="inline">二合</note>斛<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b10"/><lg id="lgX02p0836b1001"><l>次結車輅印</l><l>定慧仰相叉</l><l>以右押於左</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b11"/><l>禪智捻進力</l><l>最下<note n="0836002" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">弟疑第</note>弟一文</l><l>旋轉送向前</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b12"/><l>想成寶車輅</l><l>念彼真言曰</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b13"/><p id="pX02p0836b1301" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0836003" resp="Xuzangjing" place="foot text" type="orig">觀疑&CB00418;</note>觀魯都魯吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b14"/><p id="pX02p0836b1401">三遍或七遍。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b15"/><lg id="lgX02p0836b1501"><l>想尊乘車輅</l><l>徐來降道場</l><l>住於&CB00980;空中</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b16"/><l>待請而來入</l><l>不違本誓願</l><l>念彼真言曰</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b17"/><p id="pX02p0836b1701" type="dharani">曩莫悉底哩野<note place="inline">四合</note>地尾<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>南怛佗<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00617;跢南<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b18"/>唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;折朗<note place="inline">二合</note>祇你也<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>揭羅灑<note place="inline">二合</note>野娑&CB00085;
<lb ed="X" n="0836b19"/><note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b20"/><lg id="lgX02p0836b2001"><l>由此真言力</l><l>及結契相應</l><l>能召於本尊</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b21"/><l>并及餘眷屬</l><l>降臨道場所</l><l>施願與行人</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b22"/><l>欲結車輅時</l><l>先當淨道路</l><l>二手捧香爐</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b23"/><l>念修祕密句</l><l>淨治&CB00980;中路</l><l>後乃請聖尊</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836b24"/><l>想香至彼宮</l><l>念彼真言曰</l></lg>
<pb ed="X" id="X02.0181.0836c" n="0836c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0836c01"/><p id="pX02p0836c0101" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>素悉地揭哩入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>理哆難多慕<note place="inline">引</note>羅多<note place="inline">去</note>曳
<lb ed="X" n="0836c02"/>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;滿他滿他賀喃吽發吒</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0836c03"/><lg id="lgX02p0836c0301"><l>若作此妙法</l><l>其空中關籥</l><l>悉皆自開解</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836c04"/><l>亦成辟除障</l><l>乃至清淨等</l><l>乃成驚覺尊</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836c05"/><l>眷屬并親近</l><l>次先作奉請</l><l>印契誦後明</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836c06"/><l>召集諸聖賢</l><l>入曼荼羅內</l><l>請召真言曰</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836c07"/><l>或三或七遍</l><l>召請入道場</l><l>慇懃陳所請</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0836c08"/><l>復請妙吉祥</l><l>密&CB00528;金剛主</l><l>定慧合蓮掌</l>
